DESCRIPTION

Create a user authentication and management system for the web.


COMPONENTS & ARCHITECTURE

use MVC pattern
Apache w/ mod_jk for http server
Tomcat for JSP/Servlet processing
PostgreSQL for RDBMS
Hibernate (potentially) as ORM


VIEWS

Register - username, password, verify password fields
Login - username, password, remember me fields
Administration - disable account, disable registration, delete account

notes: passwords are hashed using blowfish algorithm JCE appears to implement 
this.
